      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TWO FISTED (1) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 1.75 lengths from the winner Romaika in second(20.23) at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from eight starts. Winning claims. WHISKY ADDICTION (4) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 20.05 beating Lumiere. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. In top form and looks a key chance again. OPHIDIAN (7) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fifth (20.43) at this track latest. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. In the mix. CHLOE'S COMET (2) can feature with the right run.",
